.comments.collapsed
  -# { id: "widget-#{widget.id}-comments" }
  - if comments.any?
    - comments.each do |comment|
      = render partial: 'comments/comment', locals: { comment: comment }
  - if user_signed_in?
    = render partial: 'comments/signed_in_form', locals: { commentable: commentable }
  - else
    Please
    = link_to 'log in', new_user_session_path(redirect_to: url_for(commentable))
    or
    = link_to 'sign up', root_url(subdomain: 'www')
    to comment.